<H2 CLASS="western">2. Release Notes 1.3.0.m7</H2>
<H2 CLASS="western">2.1 Improvement</H2>
<P>137 - Split tool now supports the use of closed lines as a split line. </P>
<P>138 - Refactor - The SplitFeatureBuilder class was created in order to simplify the use of the split process (split plus add vertex). </P>

<H2 CLASS="western">3. Release Notes 1.3.0.m6</H2>
<H2 CLASS="western">3.1 Patch</H2>
<P>133 - Sometimes the original feature is not deleted. </P>
<P>134 - Drawing an split line using a hole's vertex does not produce the expected result </P>
<P>135 - An split line, using the geometry's vertexes that will be split, does not produce the expected features</P> 


<H2 CLASS="western">4. Release Notes 1.3.0.m5</H2>
<H2 CLASS="western">4.1 Patch</H2>
<P>87  - If the map's crs and the layer's crs are different the parallel tool does not produce any result. </P>
<P>111 - In some case the parallel tool generates “peaks” in the parallel result. </P>

<H2 CLASS="western">4.2 Improvement</H2>
<P>84  - Split must show a message when the split line has the initial point equal to the last point.   </P>
<P>122 - The behaviour required by simple spatial operations with only two parameters (source and target layer) was refactoring  in SimplePresenter and SimpleCommand.</P>


<H2 CLASS="western">5. Release Notes 1.3.0.m4</H2>
<H2 CLASS="western">5.1 Patch</H2>
<P>78 – Parallel - Perform an analisys of the resultant geometry to get rid off spurious nodes. / Realizar un análisis a la geometría resultante para eliminar nodos espúreos. </P>
<H2 CLASS="western">6. Release Notes 1.3.0.m3</H2>
<H2 CLASS="western">6.1 Patch</H2>
<P>62 – Split - Split between holes using as split line a piece of the border off one holes produces an incorrect new hole. / Split entre agujeros usando como linea de split parte del border de uno de los agujeros produce un nuevo agujero. </P>
<H2 CLASS="western">6.2 New Feature</H2>
<P>79 – Spatial Operation - Buffer. It was added the new cap styles. / Se agregaron los nuevos estilos para los "gorros" del buffer. </P>
<H2 CLASS="western">7. Release Notes 1.3.0.m2</H2>
<H2 CLASS="western">7.1 Improvement</H2>
<P>64 – Parallel - Improve parallel algorithm. / Mejorar el algoritmo de la paralela..</P>
<H2 CLASS="western">8. Release Notes 1.3.0.m1</H2>
<H2 CLASS="western">8.1 Task</H2>
<P>64 – Align with udig 1.2-m6. / Alinear con udig 1.2-m6.</P>
